                        "utilityType":  "other",
                        "description":  "Roll the d6 demon table to summon either two CR 1-or-lower demons, four CR 1/2-or-lower demons, or eight CR 1/4-or-lower demons; the GM chooses the demons and the caster places them in visible unoccupied spaces within 60 feet. The demons disappear at 0 HP or when the spell ends, are hostile to every creature, roll group initiative, pursue the nearest non-demons, and cannot cross, harm, or target creatures inside an optional blood circle that consumes the material component when the spell ends.",
